Conflicts: pepperflashplugin-nonfree
Replaces: pepperflashplugin-nonfree
Description: Pepper Flash Player - browser plugin
 This package will download and unpack the PPAPI flash plugin from Adobe,
 and add configuration files for chromium and 
 browser-plugin-freshplayer-pepperflash.
 The end user license agreement is available at Adobe.
 This package itself does not contain any software from Adobe.
 .
 NOTE: no checksum verification of the downloaded file is performed.
 
